a v Tokaii kolem 18 °C.

39
00:07:04,175 --> 00:07:05,134
Jdu do práce.

40
00:08:44,567 --> 00:08:47,737
Ještě trochu... dobrý.

41
00:08:56,871 --> 00:08:59,206
Takhle... Dobrý.

42
