622
01:11:17,566 --> 01:11:19,234
Sladké s oříšky.

623
01:11:19,234 --> 01:11:20,402
Ne, díky.

624
01:11:20,611 --> 01:11:22,321
- Vem si.
- To je dobrý.

625
