731
01:21:21,795 --> 01:21:23,129
Budeme pokračovat?

732
01:21:24,547 --> 01:21:25,548
Budeme.

733
01:21:28,593 --> 01:21:30,929
Tak jo, zkouška.

734
01:21:36,226 --> 01:21:39,104
<i>Bude se zkoušet!</i>

735
01:21:39,104 --> 01:21:40,313
